Well, I suppose we'd better
get down to details?

64
00:07:49,009 --> 00:07:51,136
啊，实干的男人，就像我哥一样
Ah, a practical man. Just like brother.

65
00:07:51,912 --> 00:07:53,470
广告上说“价格合理”
The ad did say "reasonable".

