I'm coming apart, as you can see...

117
00:10:58,921 --> 00:11:01,788
- 噢，哥哥...
- 哦吼，哥哥没事
- Oh, brother...
- Oh, brother is right.

118
00:11:03,292 --> 00:11:05,319
你喜欢吗？
Well, do you like it?

119
00:11:05,995 --> 00:11:08,259
- 我们喜欢
- 真的吗？
- We love it.
- Really?

120
00:11:09,464 --> 00:11:11,697
